Short Title: National Institute of Standards and Technology for the Future Act of 2021
Long Title: To reauthorize the National Institute of Standards and Technology, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Amend the Code for Marriage Equality Act of 2021
Long Title: To replace references to "wives" and "husbands" in Federal law with references to "spouses", and for other purposes.

Short Title: REPAIR Act Renew Effective Protection of Americans’ Information Rights Act Do Not Track Act Data Privacy Bill of Rights Act
Long Title: To protect the privacy of internet users by reinforcing online privacy rights and through the establishment of a national Do Not Track system, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Reproductive Health Care Accessibility Act
Long Title: To amend the Public Health Service Act to improve reproductive health care of individuals with disabilities.

Short Title: New Business Preservation Act
Long Title: To establish the Innovation and Startups Equity Investment Program in the Department of the Treasury, through which the Secretary of the Treasury shall allocate money to certain States to assist high-potential scalable startups access venture capital to commercialize innovations, create jobs, and accelerate economic growth, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Better Data for Cleaner Air Act of 2022
Long Title: To protect clean air and public health by expanding fenceline and ambient air monitoring and access to air quality information for communities affected by air pollution, to require hazardous air pollutant monitoring at the fenceline of facilities whose emissions are linked to local health threats, to ensure the Environmental Protection Agency promulgates rules that require hazardous air pollutant data measurement and electronic submission at fencelines and stacks of industrial source categories, to expand and strengthen the national ambient air quality monitoring network, to deploy air sensors in communities affected by air pollution, and for other purposes.

Short Title: 9–8–8 and Parity Assistance Act of 2022
Long Title: To provide for improvements in the implementation of the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline, and for other purposes.

Short Title: College Transparency Act
Long Title: To establish a postsecondary student data system.

Short Title: Paycheck Fairness Act
Long Title: To amend the Fair Labor Standards Act of 1938 to provide more effective remedies to victims of discrimination in the payment of wages on the basis of sex, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Ocean-Based Climate Solutions Act of 2021
Long Title: To direct the Administrator of the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration to provide for ocean-based climate solutions to reduce carbon emissions and global warming; to make coastal communities more resilient; and to provide for the conservation and restoration of ocean and coastal habitats, biodiversity, and marine mammal and fish populations; and for other purposes.

Short Title: Protecting America’s Workers Act
Long Title: To amend the Occupational Safety and Health Act of 1970 to expand coverage under the Act, to increase protections for whistleblowers, to increase penalties for high gravity violations, to adjust penalties for inflation, to provide rights for victims or their family members, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Securing America’s Mineral Supply Chains Act of 2022
Long Title: To streamline hardrock mine permitting on Federal lands, support technological and scientific advancements for mineral development, expand the mining workforce, track global supply chains, strengthen domestic refining and processing capacity, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Pathways to Health Careers Act
Long Title: To provide low-income individuals with opportunities to enter and follow a career pathway in the health professions, to extend and expand demonstration projects, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Health Security and Countering Weapons of Mass Destruction Act
Long Title: To amend the Homeland Security Act of 2002 to authorize the Office of Health Security, make technical corrections to the authorization of the Countering Weapons of Mass Destruction Office, establish a Countering Weapons of Mass Destruction Advisory Committee, establish a departmental biodefense strategy, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Jobs for Economic Recovery Act of 2021
Long Title: To amend the Social Security Act to establish a new employment, training, and supportive services program for unemployed and underemployed individuals, including individuals with barriers to employment and those who are unemployed or underemployed as a result of COVID-19, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Voter Empowerment Act of 2021
Long Title: To modernize voter registration, promote access to voting for individuals with disabilities, protect the ability of individuals to exercise the right to vote in elections for Federal office, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Public Health Air Quality Act of 2022
Long Title: To protect clean air and public health by expanding fenceline and ambient air monitoring and access to air quality information for communities affected by air pollution, to require hazardous air pollutant monitoring at the fenceline of facilities whose emissions are linked to local health threats, to ensure the Environmental Protection Agency promulgates rules that require hazardous air pollutant data measurement and electronic submission at fencelines and stacks of industrial source categories, to expand and strengthen the national ambient air quality monitoring network, to deploy air sensors in communities affected by air pollution, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Roadmap to Congressional Reform Act
Long Title: To withhold the salaries of Members of Congress upon failure to agree to a budget resolution, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Stop Corporate Capture Act
Long Title: To amend title 5, United States Code, to require disclosure of conflicts of interest with respect to rulemaking, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Housing Is a Human Right Act of 2021
Long Title: To address root causes of homelessness, meet the needs of community members experiencing harms from homelessness, transition communities towards providing housing for all, end penalization of homelessness, and ensure full democratic participation and inclusion of persons experiencing homelessness, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Housing for All Act of 2022
Long Title: To address the homelessness and housing crises, to move toward the goal of providing for a home for all Americans, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Elizabeth Dole Home and Community Based Services for Veterans and Caregivers Act of 2022 Elizabeth Dole Home Care Act
Long Title: To amend title 38, United States Code, to improve certain programs of the Department of Veterans Affairs for home and community based services for veterans, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Emergency Economic and Workforce System Resiliency Act
Long Title: To direct the Secretary of Labor to award formula and competitive grants for layoff aversion activities, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Child Care for Working Families Act
Long Title: To amend the Child Care and Development Block Grant Act of 1990 and the Head Start Act to promote child care and early learning, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Websites and Software Applications Accessibility Act
Long Title: To establish uniform accessibility standards for websites and applications of employers, employment agencies, labor organizations, joint labor-management committees, public entities, public accommodations, testing entities, and commercial providers, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Save Education Jobs Act
Long Title: To authorize the establishment of an Education Jobs Fund to retain and create education jobs in communities most impacted by COVID-19, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Patsy T. Mink and Louise M. Slaughter Gender Equity in Education Act of 2021
Long Title: To support educational entities in fully implementing title IX and reducing and preventing sex discrimination in all areas of education, and for other purposes.

Short Title: SAFE Act of 2022 Save Americans from the Fentanyl Emergency Act of 2022
Long Title: To amend the Controlled Substances Act with respect to fentanyl-related substances, and for other purposes.

Short Title: MORE Act Marijuana Opportunity Reinvestment and Expungement Act
Long Title: To decriminalize and deschedule cannabis, to provide for reinvestment in certain persons adversely impacted by the War on Drugs, to provide for expungement of certain cannabis offenses, and for other purposes.

Short Title: TRUE EQUITY Act Transformational Reforms and Updates to Ensure Educational Quality and Urgent Investments in Today's Youth Act of 2021
Long Title: To provide for a Federal partnership to ensure educational equity and quality.

Short Title: Free Credit Scores for Consumers Act of 2021
Long Title: To establish requirements relating to credit scores and educational credit scores, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Restoring Community Input and Public Protections in Oil and Gas Leasing Act of 2021
Long Title: To amend the Mineral Leasing Act to make certain adjustments in leasing on Federal lands for oil and gas drilling, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Long-Term Unemployment Elimination Act of 2021
Long Title: To establish jobs programs for long-term unemployed workers, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Compensation for Americans Act of 2021
Long Title: To initiate negotiations for a bilateral agreement on compensation between the United States and the People's Republic of China relating to the spread of the virus responsible for COVID-19, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Advancing Tribal Parity on Public Land Act
Long Title: To protect Native cultural sites located on Federal land, to improve consultation with Indian Tribes, to bring parity to Indian Tribes with regard to Federal public land management laws, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Border Security for America Act of 2021
Long Title: To secure the international borders of the United States, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Billionaire Minimum Income Tax Act
Long Title: To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to impose a minimum tax on certain wealthy taxpayers that takes into account unrealized gains.

Short Title: Affordable HOME Act Affordable Housing Opportunities Made Equitable Act
Long Title: To make housing affordable, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Sustaining Our Democracy Act
Long Title: To establish a democracy advancement and innovation program, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Federal Correctional Facilities COVID–19 Response Act
Long Title: To establish procedures related to the coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) in correctional facilities.

Short Title: MRRRI Act Mississippi River Restoration and Resilience Initiative Act
Long Title: To establish the Mississippi River Restoration and Resilience Initiative to carry out projects for the protection and restoration of the Mississippi River Corridor, and for other purposes.

Short Title: End Polluter Welfare Act of 2021
Long Title: To eliminate certain subsidies for fossil-fuel production.

Short Title: Truth and Healing Commission on Indian Boarding School Policies Act
Long Title: To establish the Truth and Healing Commission on Indian Boarding School Policies in the United States, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Women in Criminal Justice Reform Act
Long Title: To provide for improvements in the treatment of women in the criminal justice system.

Short Title: REPAIR Act Reinventing Economic Partnerships And Infrastructure Redevelopment Act
Long Title: To facilitate efficient investments and financing of infrastructure projects and new, long-term job creation through the establishment of an Infrastructure Financing Authority, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Northern Rockies Ecosystem Protection Act
Long Title: To designate certain National Forest System lands and certain public lands under the jurisdiction of the Secretary of the Interior in the States of Idaho, Montana, Oregon, Washington, and Wyoming as wilderness, wild and scenic rivers, wildland recovery areas, and biological connecting corridors, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Securing Access for the central Valley and Enhancing (SAVE) Water Resources Act Reclamation Infrastructure Finance and Innovation Act
Long Title: To promote water supply reliability and improved water management for rural communities, the State of California, and the Nation, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Approving certain regulations to implement provisions of the Congressional Accountability Act of 1995 relating to the Family and Medical Leave Act of 1993 with respect to employees of the House of Representatives covered under section 202 of the Act and relating to the Fair Labor Standards Act of 1938 with respect to employees of the House of Representatives covered under section 203 of the Act, and for other purposes.
Long Title: Approving certain regulations to implement provisions of the Congressional Accountability Act of 1995 relating to the Family and Medical Leave Act of 1993 with respect to employees of the House of Representatives covered under section 202 of the Act and relating to the Fair Labor Standards Act of 1938 with respect to employees of the House of Representatives covered under section 203 of the Act, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Stronger Child Abuse Prevention and Treatment Act
Long Title: To reauthorize the Child Abuse Prevention and Treatment Act, and for other purposes.

Short Title: End Outsourcing Act
Long Title: To provide incentives for businesses to keep jobs in America, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Public Health Emergency Privacy Act
Long Title: To protect the privacy of health information during a national health emergency.

Short Title: Federal Information Security Modernization Act of 2022
Long Title: To modernize Federal information security management and improve Federal cybersecurity to combat persisting and emerging threats, and for other purposes.

Short Title: RISE Act Retirement Improvement and Savings Enhancement Act of 2021
Long Title: To improve and enhance retirement savings, and for other purposes.

Short Title: GLOBE Act of 2021 Greater Leadership Overseas for the Benefit of Equality Act of 2021
Long Title: To protect human rights and enhance opportunities for LGBTQI people around the world, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Jobs to Fight COVID–19 Act of 2021
Long Title: To establish an initiative for national testing, contact tracing, and pandemic response, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Freshwater Mussel Conservation Fund Act of 2021 Pacific Islands Plant Conservation Fund Act of 2021 North America Butterfly Conservation Fund Act of 2021 Southwest Desert Fish Conservation Fund Act of 2021
Long Title: To create dedicated funds to conserve butterflies in North America, plants in the Pacific Islands, freshwater mussels in the United States, and desert fish in the Southwest United States, and for other purposes.

Short Title: International Human Rights Defense Act of 2021
Long Title: To establish in the Bureau of Democracy, Human Rights, and Labor of the Department of State a Special Envoy for the Human Rights of LGBTQI Peoples, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Modernizing the Collegiate Student Athlete Experience Act
Long Title: To establish a government corporation to oversee student athlete agents and third-party licensees of student athlete publicity rights, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Pregnant Women in Custody Act
Long Title: To address the health needs of incarcerated women related to pregnancy and childbirth, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Southern Nevada Economic Development and Conservation Act
Long Title: To provide for conservation and economic development in the State of Nevada, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Protecting Our Kids Act
Long Title: To amend title 18, United States Code, to provide for an increased age limit on the purchase of certain firearms, prevent gun trafficking, modernize the prohibition on untraceable firearms, encourage the safe storage of firearms, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Universal School Meals Program Act of 2021
Long Title: To amend the Child Nutrition Act of 1966 and the Richard B. Russell National School Lunch Act to make breakfasts and lunches free for all children, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Social Security Stabilization and Enhancement Act
Long Title: To enhance Social Security benefits and ensure the long-term solvency of the Social Security program.

Short Title: EDUCATORS for America Act
Long Title: To reauthorize title II of the Higher Education Act of 1965, and for other purposes.

Short Title: Prohibiting Anticompetitive Mergers Act of 2022
Long Title: To prohibit certain anticompetitive mergers, to amend the Clayton Act to permit the Federal Trade Commission and the Department of Justice to reject proposed acquisitions, to implement procedures for retrospective reviews and breaking up anticompetitive consummated acquisitions, and for other purposes.
